cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with generating photo-realistic imagery of a target person in a novel pose and combining it with the scene to enhance realism. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.GR (Graphics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also uses generative networks, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves training a personalized model, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
